description: A group of kids uncover supernatural mysteries.
A battle for the Iron Throne in Westeros.
A teacher turns to cooking meth.
A bounty hunter in the Star Wars universe.
A monster hunter in a magical realm.
The life of six friends in New York.
The reign of Queen Elizabeth II.
The rise of a gangster family.
Hilarious antics in a police precinct.
The god of mischief on adventures.
Crime and family in the Ozarks.
The legal world after Breaking Bad.
